=========================
Color Commentary Teletype
=========================

NYCResistor restored a Teletype Model 15 and repurposed it to print comments from twitter matching a particular keyword.

Full writeup here: http://www.nycresistor.com/2010/04/06/nycrteletype/

NOTE: This code is a bit hacky. Use as your own risk. :)

